{"type":"message","id":"0531ddf9","parentId":"5ef2a1eb","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:17:36.410Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the email from \"Royal Cove\" was actually from donotreply@rentmanager.com with the subject \"Application Account Access\". It's about an online rental application for Royal Cove apartments. An account was created for Bobby (Robert Galletta) and he needs to verify and finish creating his account by clicking a link.\n\nLet me summarize this clearly for Bobby.","thinkingSignature":"d42b3b717fa40e4f59c8be4b06c6bb3e3b75b68913b22f23e921864eb638f117"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThat's from **Royal Cove** (via rentmanager.com) — it's about your apartment application. Here's what it says:\n\n---\n\n**Subject:** Application Account Access\n\n**From:** donotreply@rentmanager.com\n\n**What it says:**\n> Hello Robert Galletta,\n>\n> You are receiving this email as part of an online application for Royal Cove. As part of the application process, an account has been created for you using this email address. Please use the following link to **verify and finish creating your account**.\n>\n> If you did not make this request, no further action is required.\n>\n> — Jessica Ciancanelli, Royal Cove (royalcove@lexingtonpg.com)\n\n---\n\nIt's basically asking you to click a link to **complete your account setup** for the Royal Cove rental application. There's a \"Finalize\" button/link in the email.\n\nAre you in the middle of applying for Royal Cove? Let me know if you need help with the account setup or anything else! 🦋📧"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1684,"output":280,"cacheRead":28192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30156,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777090653423,"responseId":"063b735d70b09c620048b3c8fe9b096d"}}
