{"type":"message","id":"0cff8b37","parentId":"cbb97055","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:30:08.704Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_4qce7amhh70i_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: apple-notes\ndescription: Create, view, edit, delete, search, move, or export Apple Notes via the memo CLI on macOS.\nhomepage: https://github.com/antoniorodr/memo\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"emoji\": \"📝\",\n        \"os\": [\"darwin\"],\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"memo\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"brew\",\n              \"kind\": \"brew\",\n              \"formula\": \"antoniorodr/memo/memo\",\n              \"bins\": [\"memo\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install memo via Homebrew\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# Apple Notes CLI\n\nUse `memo notes` to manage Apple Notes directly from the terminal. Create, view, edit, delete, search, move notes between folders, and export to HTML/Markdown.\n\nSetup\n\n- Install (Homebrew): `brew tap antoniorodr/memo && brew install antoniorodr/memo/memo`\n- Manual (pip): `pip install .` (after cloning the repo)\n- macOS-only; if prompted, grant Automation access to Notes.app.\n\nView Notes\n\n- List all notes: `memo notes`\n- Filter by folder: `memo notes -f \"Folder Name\"`\n- Search notes (fuzzy): `memo notes -s \"query\"`\n\nCreate Notes\n\n- Add a new note: `memo notes -a`\n  - Opens an interactive editor to compose the note.\n- Quick add with title: `memo notes -a \"Note Title\"`\n\nEdit Notes\n\n- Edit existing note: `memo notes -e`\n  - Interactive selection of note to edit.\n\nDelete Notes\n\n- Delete a note: `memo notes -d`\n  - Interactive selection of note to delete.\n\nMove Notes\n\n- Move note to folder: `memo notes -m`\n  - Interactive selection of note and destination folder.\n\nExport Notes\n\n- Export to HTML/Markdown: `memo notes -ex`\n  - Exports selected note; uses Mistune for markdown processing.\n\nLimitations\n\n- Cannot edit notes containing images or attachments.\n- Interactive prompts may require terminal access.\n\nNotes\n\n- macOS-only.\n- Requires Apple Notes.app to be accessible.\n- For automation, grant permissions in System Settings > Privacy & Security > Automation.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1777091408704}}
{"type":"message","id":"099c8edd","parentId":"0cff8b37","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:30:12.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me save the draft to Apple Notes using memo CLI.","thinkingSignature":"70c48495deb5dd34a51aa5bf3ddfaec350f7f76c1b2009e3895d6bd7a2da5347"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pbqjy00eizck_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo -e \"Royal Cove Reply Draft\\n\\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\\n\\nHi Amy,\\n\\nThank you for getting back to me! Logan and I are very interested in the 1 Bedroom / 1 Bath option starting at $1,825. A few questions before we apply:\\n\\nScreening Process:\\nWhat exactly do I need to provide for the screening? I know you mentioned a credit check, background check, and pet screening — but specifically what documents are required?\\n\\nProof of Income:\\nWhat do you accept as proof of income? I can provide pay stubs, but wanted to confirm what's needed.\\n\\nRhino Partner Program:\\nYou mentioned Rhino as an alternative to an upfront cash deposit — how does that work exactly? Is it just a monthly fee instead of a deposit?\\n\\nWaiver Program:\\nCan you explain what the $18/month Waiver Program covers? What are the benefits?\\n\\nApplying:\\nI would like to move forward with the application. Please let me know the next steps.\\n\\nIn-Person Tour:\\nI originally mentioned coming up to tour in person, but unfortunately that won't be possible for me. Would it be possible for my friend Angel to tour the unit on our behalf before we finalize everything? She would be able to FaceTime us during the tour so we could see it remotely.\\n\\nThank you so much for your help!\\n\\nBobby\" | memo notes -a \"Royal Cove Reply Draft\"","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":563,"output":351,"cacheRead":39968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40882,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777091408706,"responseId":"063b765060a11c2378f0930b9d9c9690"}}
