{"type":"message","id":"4f85dadd","parentId":"bc403ef7","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:30:52.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the folder was created. Now let me create the note in that folder.","thinkingSignature":"fe80bab1196937e7025add9f3e46dac8c789649ab47542c720f57d335b6206bf"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8l7dd4psfdcb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'APPLESCRIPT' | osascript -\ntell application \"Notes\"\n    activate\n    tell account \"iCloud\"\n        set draftFolder to folder \"OpenClaw Drafts\"\n        set theBody to \"Subject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy,\n\nThank you for getting back to me! Logan and I are very interested in the 1 Bedroom / 1 Bath option starting at $1,825. A few questions before we apply:\n\nScreening Process:\nWhat exactly do I need to provide for the screening? I know you mentioned a credit check, background check, and pet screening — but specifically what documents are required?\n\nProof of Income:\nWhat do you accept as proof of income? I can provide pay stubs, but wanted to confirm what's needed.\n\nRhino Partner Program:\nYou mentioned Rhino as an alternative to an upfront cash deposit — how does that work exactly? Is it just a monthly fee instead of a deposit?\n\nWaiver Program:\nCan you explain what the $18/month Waiver Program covers? What are the benefits?\n\nApplying:\nI would like to move forward with the application. Please let me know the next steps.\n\nIn-Person Tour:\nI originally mentioned coming up to tour in person, but unfortunately that won't be possible for me. Would it be possible for my friend Angel to tour the unit on our behalf before we finalize everything? She would be able to FaceTime us during the tour so we could see it remotely.\n\nThank you so much for your help!\n\nBobby\"\n        make new note at end of draftFolder with properties {name:\"Royal Cove Reply Draft\", body:theBody}\n    end tell\nend tell\nAPPLESCRIPT\n","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":152,"output":393,"cacheRead":41344,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41889,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777091448655,"responseId":"063b767971afba121efff34004bdc9a4"}}
