{"type":"message","id":"a6b707da","parentId":"b1e0c152","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:35:44.260Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Bobby wants to see the final formatted version of the email he'll be sending. He wants to see it formatted nicely as it would appear in the email. Let me also update the Apple Notes note with the edited version, then show him the clean version.","thinkingSignature":"b070129304fa7c8040505c76911ef380c0fb3b9a11759070f2e9388b4739eba3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_d8y3jzsyyqj0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'APPLESCRIPT' | osascript -\ntell application \"Notes\"\n    activate\n    set theBody to \"Subject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy,\n\nThank you for getting back to me! Logan and I are very interested in the 1 Bedroom / 1 Bath option starting at $1,825. A few questions before we apply:\n\nScreening Process:\nWhat exactly do I need to provide?\n\nProof of Income:\nWhat forms of proof of income will you need?\n\nRhino Partner Program:\nYou mentioned Rhino as an alternative to an upfront cash deposit — what is this and how does that work?\n\nWaiver Program:\nWhat is this?\n\nApplying:\nI would like to move forward with the application. Please let me know the next steps.\n\nIn-Person Tour:\nI originally mentioned coming up to tour in person, but unfortunately that won't be possible for me. Would it be possible for my friend Angel to tour the unit on our behalf before we finalize everything? She would be able to FaceTime us during the tour so we could see it remotely.\n\nThank you so much for your help!\n\nBobby\"\n    set noteName to \"Royal Cove Reply Draft\"\n    set draftFolder to folder \"OpenClaw Drafts\"\n    -- delete existing note\n    set existingNote to first note of draftFolder whose name is noteName\n    set body of existingNote to theBody\nend tell\nAPPLESCRIPT\n","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42480,"output":376,"cacheRead":352,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43208,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777091732509,"responseId":"063b779403dd880c0ca5003b9fe34c32"}}
