{"type":"message","id":"f17f94e6","parentId":"8a221bdc","timestamp":"2026-04-25T04:37:10.481Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image tool can't access the Desktop path. Let me try sending the image through the message tool or use a different approach. Actually, let me just describe what I'm seeing since I can't get the screenshot image analyzed.\n\nLet me try a different approach - I'll write the email content to a file and show it to Bobby in a nicely formatted way, or I can try to attach it to a message.\n\nActually, the simplest thing here is just to tell Bobby how the email will look - I've already shown him the formatted version in my previous message. The issue is he wants to see it in iCloud Mail interface. Since the browser is logged in, maybe Bobby can just tell me what's on screen.\n \nI think the best approach is to just copy the email text to his clipboard so he can paste it into iCloud Mail himself. That way he can see exactly how it looks when it arrives.","thinkingSignature":"959dcd5dd69b3b0232a8952039f099a2659eb8dcf3f10817fc055a6102ac229b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\nI've got the screenshot but I can't view it from here. Let me copy the email text to your clipboard so you can paste it into iCloud Mail — that way you can preview exactly what it'll look like when received:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_azgcrcyrmaxj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo -n 'To: rtg.bobby@icloud.com\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHi Amy,\n\nThank you for getting back to me! Logan and I are very interested in the 1 Bedroom / 1 Bath option starting at $1,825. A few questions before we apply:\n\nScreening Process:\nWhat exactly do I need to provide?\n\nProof of Income:\nWhat forms of proof of income will you need?\n\nRhino Partner Program:\nYou mentioned Rhino as an alternative to an upfront cash deposit — what is this and how does that work?\n\nWaiver Program:\nWhat is this?\n\nApplying:\nI would like to move forward with the application. Please let me know the next steps.\n\nIn-Person Tour:\nI originally mentioned coming up to tour in person, but unfortunately that won't be possible for me. Would it be possible for my friend Angel to tour the unit on our behalf before we finalize everything? She would be able to FaceTime us during the tour so we could see it remotely.\n\nThank you so much for your help!\n\nBobby' | pbcopy && echo \"Copied!\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":147,"output":484,"cacheRead":44896,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45527,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777091826965,"responseId":"063b77f3907cd096de2712a2af5a79e6"}}
